// mobile/ios/Config/Local.xcconfig
//
// PR-Sprint7-Item-13 (MOB-6) — Local (dev / debug) build configuration.
//
// This file is wired in via `baseConfigurationReference` on the Debug
// build configurations in `Runner.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj`. It holds
// per-environment build settings that must NOT ship to App Store / Test
// Flight distribution builds.
//
// Design notes
// ------------
// * `TEAMS_IDENTIFIER` is intentionally empty: simulator + dev builds do
//   not require a real Apple Developer Team ID for code signing (Xcode
//   falls back to "Sign to Run Locally"). An empty value here keeps the
//   local dev loop friction-free and ensures we never accidentally embed
//   a production team ID in a debug build that an attacker could
//   reverse-engineer (defence-in-depth alongside §A anonymisation).
// * The matching Release xcconfig (`Production.xcconfig`) carries the
//   real team ID. See `docs/SETUP-iOS.md` for the procedure to populate
//   it from App Store Connect.
// * `DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = $(TEAMS_IDENTIFIER)` in the project file (H3-H8)
//   picks up the empty value here so dev builds skip team-based signing.
// * Xcode does NOT auto-substitute `$(...)` strings in `.entitlements`
//   files. The literal `$(TEAMS_IDENTIFIER)` placeholder in
//   `Runner/Runner.entitlements` and
//   `NetworkExtension/OpenE2eeTunnelProvider.entitlements` therefore
//   requires either a build-phase substitution script (recommended for
//   CI) or manual replacement before the very first App Store upload.
//   The Local config empty value means dev builds still sign cleanly
//   even when the literal placeholder remains in the entitlements file.
//
// Pre-flight (from ios-native-bridging.md)
// ----------------------------------------
// Verify before changing `baseConfigurationReference`:
//   * This file is referenced by PBXFileReference UUID B8 in pbxproj.
//   * It is the base config for XCBuildConfiguration entries H3, H5,
//     H7, H8 (Debug + RunnerTests Release). The H4 + H6 Release
//     configurations point at `Production.xcconfig` instead.

TEAMS_IDENTIFIER =
OPENE2EE_BUILD_ENVIRONMENT = local